story.storyDescription: Sarah finds a dead body in the woods and uncovers a dark and deadly mystery.
story.title: Littlefield - Part 7

messages.text: Mom, are you there??
Was just about to text you
Listen, is that man still at the house?
You knew he was here?
Yes. He has it out for me.
Listen, if he’s still there, get him to leave.
Helena and I have to come get you to bring you to safety
What do you mean?
Something bad is happening right now that hasn’t yet reached the house.
Just go to the attic, and when we’re out front, we will text and come get you.
Well, you’re right, something else bad is happening right now.
Are you okay?? Did he hurt, or threaten you??
Also, you should know he’s not leaving
What!? Just tell him you don’t know where I am or lie that I’m somewhere else
This is a bit of a latergram from your basement, but:
LET HER GO LUKE!
See, the thing is, you piece of shit, your Mom and I are already on the road.
She’s driving my car right now.
My glock is pointed at her lovely flower-patterned side.
I TOLD YOU I DON’T HAVE WHAT YOU WANT, LET HER GO!
We’re about to go back to a warehouse...
where we can have a bit of a powwow, until you bring me my money.
I don’t have your money!!
Your Mom doesn’t have money.
You know she has a bit of an online gambling habit?
ANYWAY. I know you have it and are hiding it...
and now I also know you slipped out the back door like a pussy.
That makes me mad.
I told you I gave the money to Sarah to give to you
Yeah, well I think you know where she is right now too motherfucker
If you tell me where she is, I’ll let your Mom go.
She has nothing to do with this!!
AND YOU SHOULD KNOW I’M WITH THE COPS RIGHT NOW
Oh? Well tell them anything, and her brains are going to be on my window.
Now, tell me where Sarah is, and I won’t shoot her
I just heard that she’s at a place called The Barn
Which is located where.
It’s off of 95 and Whitvale Pike. It’s gated apparently.
I don’t know how we get in or even if we can get in.
All I know is the cops won’t even look for her there.
Okay, so here’s what’s going to happen.
You’re going to meet us at the Burger King on Tisdale...
and we’re going to go there together
How the fuck am I supposed to get there!!?
I told you I’m with the cops right now.
If you haven’t noticed...
there is a problem with these fucking dead people roaming around eating other people
I was offered human meat once, while I was doing a deal in China. Tastes like duck.
Anyway - I don’t know what you’re talking about.
And sounds like a high school bullshit lie to me.
I’m not lying. And I don’t know how I’m going to get to meet you.
I’m parked in Sarah’s family’s driveway right now in a cop van
Steal a car
You want me to STEAL the van???
Is the family car still in the driveway? The chevy cavalier?
There are keys in the glove box.
You see, I stopped there first.
It’s still there.
So…get out of the little car you’re in now you twat and get over here
They are going to be out with her parents any minute now
SO THEN FUCKING RUN!
DO YOU UNDERSTAND THAT I’M GOING TO SHOOT THE SHIT OUT OF YOUR MOTHER IF YOU DON’T
Okay, I’m going…
AND NO COPS! The second I see cops, she’s done.
OKAY
Hurry the fuck up
You get in the car??
ANSWER ME!
YES! I’m in!!
Sorry I can’t multitask fucking thieving a friend’s Dad’s car, and texting.
Did anyone see you??
Just my friend Helena. But not the cops.
They were inside still.
I’m pulling off Columbus now to Echo Lake.
Once I see you pull that car into the parking lot at BK alone, we’ll pull in.
Now hurry. You have ten minutes.
